# Wiesn-Agent 🍺
# AI-powered Oktoberfest reservation agent

# ── Provider: GitHub Models (free) ────────────────────
# Create a GitHub PAT with `models:read` permission:
# https://github.com/settings/tokens → "Generate new token"
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

# Model (free via GitHub Models)
# Recommended: gpt-4o, gpt-4o-mini, Meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct, Mistral-small
GITHUB_MODEL=gpt-4o

# ── API Auth (optional) ──────────────────────────────
# Set a token to require auth on all /api/ endpoints.
# When empty/unset, the API is open (suitable for localhost-only use).
# WIESN_API_TOKEN=your-secret-token-here
